  Page body copy lives in the Shopify page editor (rich text).
  Structured visual components live here as section settings + blocks.

  CONTENT FLOW:
  Hero ‚Üí Preview Banner ‚Üí {{ page.content }} ‚Üí Style Recommendations ‚Üí
  Photo Tips ‚Üí Products ‚Üí FAQ ‚Üí Final CTA

  REUSE:
  One section file, one CSS file. Each breed gets its own JSON template.
  Section + CSS never change; content varies per template.
